{"tid":1514304,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"To 呂小姐","createTime":"2019-08-28T16:34:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T17:22:27.000Z","uid":137833,"like":52,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"1a29e0174f2239fa739b07682e74ed1c326e3f2f","tid":1514304,"uid":137833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:34:24.000Z","msg":"你好叻女呀，多謝你肯企出嚟揭發班死黑警。有你做榜樣，其他受害人都開始肯講返自己嘅經歷，多謝你咁勇敢呀。<br />\n<br />\n同埋唔好再道歉啦，你已經好叻啦。慢慢抖下啦，<br />\n等自己ready好先再一齊繼續出啦。應承我哋唔好自責得唔得？今日喺集會，相信你都見到個個手足幾支持你，幾錫你。所以要記住記住，冇人怪你呀！<br />\n<br />\n仲有班黑警為咗扮清白，一定會繼續講埋啲難聽說話。但係你要記住呀，我吔個個都信你，唔信啲狗，所以唔洗擔心㗎。我哋個個都一定支持你，you are not alone! 撐住呀！<br />\n<br />\n最後一句，我吔煲底見。"},{"pid":"a368f8aa1ab4175c5a673bd80e4e7fd359b3fb51","tid":1514304,"uid":212182,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:38:19.000Z","msg":"你好勇敢！保持盼望！懲罰佢地既日子近了！"},{"pid":"e99944f2daff34f93e32e5ea6121f41aa214bba9","tid":1514304,"uid":313174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:40:49.000Z","msg":"因為你地挺身而出，香港才有希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人永遠支持你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f407857f29a53ab7f7ceef342902346bc99363cf","tid":1514304,"uid":124824,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T16:41:26.000Z","msg":"所有呂受害人 <br />\n你地真係好叻女...比我攬下你地<br />\n我知你地一定好辛苦 活係黑暗底下<br />\n你地抖下啦 之後交比我地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"358be8c3fa9b66acc5ade27ff9d22c02dea02dd1","tid":1514304,"uid":124824,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f407857f29a53ab7f7ceef342902346bc99363cf","tid":1514304,"uid":124824,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score"